entries.name: ResolutionState
entries.desc:
A state that a {Resolution} can be in @attr [String] name the name of the
current requirement @attr [Array<Object>] requirements currently
unsatisfied requirements @attr [DependencyGraph] activated the graph of
activated dependencies @attr [Object] requirement the current requirement
@attr [Object] possibilities the possibilities to satisfy the current
requirement @attr [Integer] depth the depth of the resolution @attr
[Set<Object>] conflicts unresolved conflicts
